  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Swingularity</strong> is a space golf game set across an infinite multiverse brimming with 2.5D planets, stars, and celestial hazards. Bogey, par, or birdie your way through both tailored and procedurally generated courses. Let the cosmos become your fairway…</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3272450/extras/112ac199b18ed10c10d1afbbd97220fe.poster.avif?t=1742118867\" width=620 height=272 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3272450/extras/112ac199b18ed10c10d1afbbd97220fe.webm?t=1742118867\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3272450/extras/112ac199b18ed10c10d1afbbd97220fe.mp4?t=1742118867\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Harness the gravitational forces of Newtonian mechanics to slingshot around planets and stars. With a sophisticated space-time overlay, you can estimate the perfect angle and power for that elusive hole-in-one.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3272450/extras/46996fce6351b04a3026d9a43035dfc5.poster.avif?t=1742118867\" width=610 height=266 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3272450/extras/46996fce6351b04a3026d9a43035dfc5.webm?t=1742118867\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3272450/extras/46996fce6351b04a3026d9a43035dfc5.mp4?t=1742118867\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Forget mundane sand-traps and lakes. In <strong>Swingularity</strong>, you’ll evade the fiery heat of stars, weave through the deadly beams of quasars, and even send your ball flying through black holes. Each galaxy offers a unique combination of hazards and obstacles that challenge you to master the art of cosmic golf.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3272450/extras/c83577010e39e6dcd66dd74d3186b6bd.poster.avif?t=1742118867\" width=622 height=272 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3272450/extras/c83577010e39e6dcd66dd74d3186b6bd.webm?t=1742118867\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3272450/extras/c83577010e39e6dcd66dd74d3186b6bd.mp4?t=1742118867\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The main campaign is just the beginning! Complete the handcrafted story levels to unlock a limitless multiverse filled with procedurally generated courses. Enter any seed and discover a brand-new experience, ensuring that no two holes are ever the same.</p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Swingularity</strong> is a space golf game set across an infinite multiverse brimming with 2.5D planets, stars, and celestial hazards. Bogey, par, or birdie your way through both tailored and procedurally generated courses. Let the cosmos become your fairway…</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3272450/extras/112ac199b18ed10c10d1afbbd97220fe.poster.avif?t=1742118867\" width=620 height=272 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3272450/extras/112ac199b18ed10c10d1afbbd97220fe.webm?t=1742118867\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3272450/extras/112ac199b18ed10c10d1afbbd97220fe.mp4?t=1742118867\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Harness the gravitational forces of Newtonian mechanics to slingshot around planets and stars. With a sophisticated space-time overlay, you can estimate the perfect angle and power for that elusive hole-in-one.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3272450/extras/46996fce6351b04a3026d9a43035dfc5.poster.avif?t=1742118867\" width=610 height=266 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3272450/extras/46996fce6351b04a3026d9a43035dfc5.webm?t=1742118867\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3272450/extras/46996fce6351b04a3026d9a43035dfc5.mp4?t=1742118867\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Forget mundane sand-traps and lakes. In <strong>Swingularity</strong>, you’ll evade the fiery heat of stars, weave through the deadly beams of quasars, and even send your ball flying through black holes. Each galaxy offers a unique combination of hazards and obstacles that challenge you to master the art of cosmic golf.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3272450/extras/c83577010e39e6dcd66dd74d3186b6bd.poster.avif?t=1742118867\" width=622 height=272 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3272450/extras/c83577010e39e6dcd66dd74d3186b6bd.webm?t=1742118867\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3272450/extras/c83577010e39e6dcd66dd74d3186b6bd.mp4?t=1742118867\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The main campaign is just the beginning! Complete the handcrafted story levels to unlock a limitless multiverse filled with procedurally generated courses. Enter any seed and discover a brand-new experience, ensuring that no two holes are ever the same.</p>",
